The App UI designed for a design a thon for which we secured the first position:

Tripski is the best travel buddy out there .... youve now got all you need for your holiday planning in one app : ) 

  features:
  
  1. One can search through location specific hotels to stay in
  2. One can book for the respective hotels ... choosing rooms and facilities
  3. The app gives the detailed description of the selected hotel with all its available facilities 
  4. The app Provides you with exciting holiday ideas based on your Personality sweet spots
  5. The app also provides you with a daily update of all the discounts and offers offered by the various hotels
  6. The app also enables you to book activities, both indoor and outdoor, for any respective hotel once you have booked rooms for it.
  7. The app allows you to book cabs to/from the airport/railway/port
  8. In app wallet and e pay
  9. Classy Dark mode

Figma link: https://www.figma.com/file/CJOsX0EaByNqPoeczhPT0F/Hotel-Booking-UI?node-id=0%3A1
